{"tid":31933,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遭迷暈轉售作冥婚下葬時拍棺保命聾啞屍新娘復活","createTime":"2016-12-10T02:49:04.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T11:14:00.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dadbd6da0aa051c85b3d66a948cbb4e0949c7713","tid":31933,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T02:49:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20161210/large/a2201a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20161210%2Flarge%2Fa2201a.gif&h=7fb49e04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n險遭生葬的趙梅（小圖）被李姓疑犯賣作「鬼妻」。<br />\n<br />\n河南林州市原康鎮一戶人家因迷信封建，執意要為日前身亡的兒子買一具女人屍體作冥婚，便從湖南以3萬元人民幣（下同，約3.37萬港元）禮金買「屍新娘」，但已封棺、準備下葬時，棺材竟傳出拍擊的聲音，打開棺材發現屍新娘「復活」，原來她為聾啞人士、並有嚴重智障，遭冷血的不法分子從外地迷暈到河南，當作屍新娘出售。<br />\n<br />\n河南林州警方前日通報案情，當地原康鎮一名元姓男子日前因故死亡，他的家人因有封建迷信的思想，便想為兒子娶一個妻子冥婚，將二人合葬。隨後經人介紹，得知湖南有一具女屍可運來當屍新娘，該「女屍」的家人則要求3萬元的「禮金」。<br />\n<br />\n騙子收3萬「禮金」<br />\n但原來屍新娘趙梅並未死，她是聾啞人士，並有嚴重智障，不法分子發現後收留她，得知有人想要「女屍」，他們便心生邪惡的念頭，要將活人當死屍賣。到了7月中旬，其中一名王姓犯人開車帶趙梅到林州康原鎮，途中將鎮靜藥物放在礦泉水，讓趙梅喝下，待趙梅昏迷後，他便對元家謊稱自己是趙梅的兄長，趙梅已死亡，收取了3萬元後便開車離開。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20161210/large/a2201b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20161210%2Flarge%2Fa2201b.gif&h=f13b99e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n元家的人不虞有詐，便為昏迷的趙梅更換衣物、裝棺後用鐵釘封口。豈料在下葬前夕，趙梅醒來，拍打棺木，外面的人才剛剛挖開墳頭，嚇一大跳，以為屍變，想扔下挖墳的工具就逃跑，但其中一人想了想，他們人多，沒理由會怕一個死人，便壯膽走過去看，打開棺材見到仍活著的趙梅，讓她躲過死劫。警方接報追查下去，在湖南邵陽縣、衡陽市祁東縣等地，將六名涉嫌干犯故意殺人罪的疑犯拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n河南《大河報"},{"pid":"0396a7eaa3f68ea5d6d2974470878adbdc08b674","tid":31933,"uid":57489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T02:52:55.000Z","msg":"附合國情"},{"pid":"8e8384bcdff389394e88db387b76eacd87022819","tid":31933,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T03:04:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc422cd42467afeee9494de4c56cd33d75bbfc01","tid":31933,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:50:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebf61adffa0e0bb18cee060ade6ea9e03b0455aa","tid":31933,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T06:00:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bc896bf04f02eb0515b35dd902c868ad5097472","tid":31933,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T10:27:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51fcc5e021f7a38825f5eb7d79ba3300b26acc47","tid":31933,"uid":25350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T10:29:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>附合國情</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n蚹蛤蟈蜻"},{"pid":"754194808007671d5e61279246bda344bcf5b67c","tid":31933,"uid":987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T10:30:58.000Z","msg":"咩都有商機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84f3250e91bc9b1f4ff8186c6f654e7f7b71d389","tid":31933,"uid":498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T10:47:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩都有商機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果係屍變...我地咪玩緊生化危機生存玩戲"},{"pid":"087b104e54857ccba72d764fccf77e24df5793cd","tid":31933,"uid":15084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T10:59:47.000Z","msg":"強國人其實好撚有創意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係無咩人性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ba8c2cac43bfac87a23eb40e867bc890812aece","tid":31933,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T11:09:58.000Z","msg":"癡撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f6538c0dc909eab0c86cc6dd0cfe9bce19a03b1","tid":31933,"uid":7008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T11:14:00.000Z","msg":"活著比死亡更痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}